```plantuml
@startuml pagopa_pn-infra

actor User
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "Lambda Reverse Proxy" as LRP
participant "Microservice A" as MSA
participant "EventBridge" as EB
participant "SQS Queue" as SQS
participant "Microservice B" as MSB
participant "CloudWatch" as CW
participant "SNS" as SNS
participant "Slack" as SLACK

User -> APIGW: HTTP Request
APIGW -> LRP: Route Request
LRP -> MSA: Invoke Service
MSA -> EB: Emit Event
EB -> MSB: Trigger Lambda
MSB -> SQS: Send Message
SQS -> MSB: Receive Message
MSB -> CW: Log Metrics
MSB -> SNS: Publish Notification
SNS -> SLACK: Send Alert

@enduml
```